  - atc_3: Formoterol is pharmacologically related to adrenergics, inhalants and adrenergics, inhalants and adrenergics, inhalants.
  - atc_4: The chemical and functional group of  is adrenergics in combination with anticholinergics incl. triple combinations with corticosteroids and adrenergics in combination with corticosteroids or other drugs, excl. anticholinergics and selective beta-2-adrenoreceptor agonists.
